<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“安静点儿，同学们。”老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们只剩两周就要结课了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以今天，我想让你们写下暑假你们都要做些什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这很容易！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我很清楚地知道我会在这个夏天做什么，我已经迫不及待夏天的到来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要去我爷爷奶奶家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们生活在北部的一个大湖泊旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个湖永远不会太凉，它是那么清澈，我可以一直看到湖底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我太爱这湖了，所以奶奶有时干脆叫我鱼儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会在湖里游一整个早晨，直到奶奶叫我吃午饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我永远不会对游泳感到厌倦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一大早，爷爷和我会乘船去钓鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果我们幸运的话，会钓到大鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>湖面上安静而平和。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>午饭以后，有很多家务要做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我最爱的家务是帮爷爷剪草坪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他有一个大的除草车，我可以坐在上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们还会清理船只。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我爷爷会修理发动机，我会擦亮船的里面和外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>做完家务，我又去玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>去年，我在橡树上边搭了一座堡垒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一些朋友和我一起在我的树堡里玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们是约翰和缇娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们会一起做很多有趣的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我最爱的事之一是等待冰淇淋车的到来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当车来的时候，我们会从树堡里爬下来买冰淇淋甜筒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我最爱吃的是巧克力味儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗯，真好吃！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>约翰，缇娜，还有我喜欢去沙滩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在沙滩上，我们会建一个沙堡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>去年，我建了一个和我差不多高的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>五点，我会和爷爷奶奶一起吃晚饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我最爱的食物是烧烤味儿汉堡加玉米棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我奶奶是世界上最好的厨师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃过晚饭，我奶奶、爷爷，还有我会看日落。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当太阳沉入湖底时它看上去美极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上，我们会围坐在篝火旁，爷爷会给我讲故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些恐怖，有些好笑，但是都很有趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时奶奶让我在火上烤棉花糖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快我就累了，上床睡觉的时间到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我并不介意上床睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为第二天，我就能把所有的事再做一遍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我真的很喜欢……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“时间到！”老师说，“请把你们的故事交上来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哦！我还没有开始写。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>